itemDisplayDescription: "Soft tortillas stuffed with your favorite meat and toppings."
"Soft tortilla packed with your choice of meat and toppings."
"It’s everyone’s favorite-a burrito stuffed with your favorite fillings and covered with Salsarita’s creamy queso."
"A quesadilla takes all your favorite fillings and lovingly heats them with cheese in a folded soft tortilla."
"We smother our wildly addictive tortilla chips in creamy queso and pile it high with your choice of fresh toppings and meat."
"Lose the tortilla, and fill up a bowl with your favorite burrito ingredients."
"Start with a crunchy taco shell filled with Romaine lettuce and pile on your favorite, fresh ingredients. Ditch the shell for a healthier meal!"
